      "review_summary": "The PR changes Ask Molty retrieval to prefer `docs-search.json`, retry/fallback to `llms-full.txt`, preserve source/GitHub context during docs outages, add `DOCS_INDEX_URL`, and cover the runtime paths in smoke tests.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection: current main awaits the docs corpus fetch without a catch, so a 503 or invalid corpus response aborts `buildWorkspace` before usable source/GitHub context can be mounted. I did not run a local repro because this review is read-only, but the PR smoke test models the failing path directly.",
